ckquote><br />\n咁你投訴咗未先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我敢講你肯踏出第一步去投訴，佢一定要回應。你唔滿意佢回應你就推上去申訴專員公署。到最後都要交待。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你上網講係無作用。"},{"pid":"fbb6523bd5086ea7abcb9f41e543ab60b91426b5","tid":125012,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:43:04.000Z","msg":"水貨區就算吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}